<p style="Heading 1"><c props="lang:en-US"></c>AbiWord Credits</p>
<p style="Normal">AbiWord has been written by a large team of volunteers. This page acknowledges their contributions.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Original Core Developers</p>
<p style="Normal">Thomas Fletcher, Jeff Hostetler, Paul Rohr, Bob Sievers, Eric Sink, Shaw Terwilliger</p>
<p style="Heading 2">2.0 Core Developers</p>
<p style="Normal">Hubert Figuiere, Francis Franklin, Tomas Frydrych, Dom Lachowicz, Patrick Lam, Michael Pritchett, Martin Sevior, Jesper Skov, Jordi Mas, Johann Bjork, Marc Maurer, Will Lachance</p>
<p style="Heading 2">2.2 Core Developers</p>
<p style="Normal"><c props="font-family:Times New Roman; font-size:12pt; color:000000; text-decoration:none; text-position:normal; font-weight:normal; font-style:normal; lang:en-GB">Hubert Figuiere, Francis Franklin, Tomas Frydrych, Dom Lachowicz, Patrick Lam, Martin Sevior, Jordi Mas, Marc Maurer, Mark Gilbert</c></p>
<p style="Heading 2"><a xlink:href="credits.txt">Full Credits</a></p>
