<p style="Normal">Contributions: Alper Atici, Scott Bingman, John Clark, Tomas Frydrych, Mark Gilbert, Michael Johnson, Dom Lachowicz, Ryan Pavlik, Andrew Schoenhofer, Leon Stedman</p>
<p style="Normal">Perl script: Cal Arndt, Kenneth Christiansen (This script lets us use AbiWord to maintain the docs; it handles XHTML conversion.)</p>
